{"tid":1115156,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有方法唔使引入”海外”醫生又夠醫生用-醫藥分家","createTime":"2019-04-19T03:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T05:11:03.000Z","uid":4322,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e31c6336ce3251191688d8167fdc2250793e75d6","tid":1115156,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;海外&rdquo;醫生只係政府引狼入室既政策<br />\n<br />\n其實醫藥分家有無得諗？<br />\n（以下係外行人意見 有錯請大力屌）<br />\n既可以分擔醫生職責 <br />\n又可以善用藥劑師既能力<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170615/mobile/bkn-20170615161312777-0615_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170615%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170615161312777-0615_00822_001.html&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSTeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=fe944a77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170615/mobile/bkn-20170615161312777-0615_00822_001.html</a><br />\n普通傷風感冒咳可唔可以畀藥劑師配藥呢？出埋假紙<br />\n而且可以令更多醫生去專科做？<br />\n<br />\n甚至係有practicing nurse(PN)去睇症<br />\n(No offence, 但底線起碼要依家RN去考試再變PN)<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E6%8A%A4%E5%A3%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%2589%25A7%25E4%25B8%259A%25E6%258A%25A4%25E5%25A3%25AB&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSTeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=baf3027c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E6%8A%A4%E5%A3%AB</a><br />\n<br />\n咁樣再加埋加醫科生位 唔使支那醫生都夠喇屌！<br />\n醫生們是時候考慮下要犧牲下既有利益呢？<br />\n其實你地唔阻得幾耐 隨時有committee會投共<br />\n只要先例一開 畀得支那醫生落黎同你地搶位<br />\n除左病人利益受損 醫生水準參差<br />\n你地最後可能連人工福利地位都會下降<br />\n咁點解唔兩害取其輕呢？<br />\n起碼你仲有bargaining power<br />\n起碼你仲有得control <br />\n<br />\n最後去去五毛走<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxfz9H2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpxfz9H2.png&h=cf1d3f18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e3a2a89f4b06dcbae4212dc5ea194b92de4f2a5","tid":1115156,"uid":4322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"屌條link用左殘體字 自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924bb5683486fdef8bd924c787b3256c02a68aea","tid":1115156,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:45:11.000Z","msg":"外國啲長期病患食開某隻藥嘅病人只會見護士<br />\n除非病情有特變先會轉返畀醫生"},{"pid":"eac91695150c991d4f193beb071a73e8f9396511","tid":1115156,"uid":137248,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:49:32.000Z","msg":"要香港醫生同意醫藥分家難過引入外國醫生或者加醫學生人數<br />\n香港醫療搞到咁醫生自己有責任，尤其上晒位果班，淨係識保護利益，同埋覺得自己人上人，唔尊重其他專業如護士藥劑"},{"pid":"9eb713a656fce9c04588eae697095cbe4678db0d","tid":1115156,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:49:50.000Z","msg":"醫咩藥分家<br />\n連叫人唔好狗衝急症都未做到"},{"pid":"a2768a0922010838bea9b79176eb37b9206687de","tid":1115156,"uid":55542,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:01:30.000Z","msg":"我在外國，醫藥分家係煩過閪。<br />\n<br />\n睇完醫生，攞住張藥單，又覺得醫院賣得貴，周圍走去買藥，自己又唔識邊間好，所以只會買牌子藥，結果最貴的藥，又係貴過醫院。<br />\n<br />\n有時醫生開d特別的業，唔係周圍有<br />\n<br />\n有時醫生開牌子藥，間藥房無果隻牌子，問你要唔要generic藥，又唔敢買，又四圍找，，，<br />\n<br />\n屌你己經病緊，仲要周圍找藥買。點解唔可以醫生直接比藥我啊啊啊啊啊啊！"},{"pid":"398ec258aa0f6f5b9d4d40373da1f21c60f77f2d","tid":1115156,"uid":121989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9eb713a656fce9c04588eae697095cbe4678db0d","tid":1115156,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:49:50.000Z","msg":"醫咩藥分家<br />\n連叫人唔好狗衝急症都未做到"},"citedBy":0,"rep